# P-F: build artifacts that should never land in the repo. The release
# workflow produces these in the runner; they go straight to the GitHub
# Release. If someone copies one into a checkout (e.g. testing the resign
# script against an installed app), don't track it.
*.dmg
*.msi
*.exe
*.app/
*.AppImage
*.deb
